<lb n="0566c19" ed="X"/><lb n="0108a10" ed="R124"/>切</note>　帚<note place="inline">之酉切</note>　鞴<note place="inline">蒲拜切</note>　黲<note place="inline">千敢切</note>　鍬<note place="inline">七消切</note></p></cb:div>
